Elias Abbas (amụrụ na 1 Disemba 2001) bụ onye na-agụ egwu na Sweden. Abbas sonyere na Melodifestivalen 2018 ebe ọ guru egwu "Mitt Paradis". N'afọ 2017, o wepụtara egwu izizi ya "Min Queen". Na Febụwarị 2019, ya na Anis Don Demina wepụtara egwu ọhụrụ. Abbas weputara egwu "Problems", nke gosipụtara Noad, na 2019
Otu egwu mbụ ya nke afọ 2020 bụ "Big Time", nke gosipụtara Stress na K27. Ezinụlọ ya bụ ndị Palestine, ọ bụkwa nwanne onye na-eti egwu na Sweden bụ Amir Abbas.
